name: The Smudges 01
description:
The Smudges are what I sometimes use as a base starting point for my AI projects. Each AI project starts with a new smudge or other digital paintings. Although they don't have a definitive shape, they usually are representative of an image or emotion I feel when creating the Smudge. 
Each smudge is 2500x2500 pixels and will look fantastic on canvas or print. 
Verifiable on Twitter via my bio link and through my linktree also on Twitter.
